<div id="pf5088" class="pf w4f h34b" data-page-no="5088"><div class="pc pc5088 w4f h34b"><div class="t m289 xd3 h170 y2ffc ff1 fs56 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Why Do </div><div class="t me12 xd3 h170 y2a45 ff1 fs56 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Christians Give </div><div class="t m143c xc3 h170 y2428 ff1 fs56 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Offerings? </div><div class="t m45a xd3 h59 y509 ff4 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">111 To ensure God&apos;s continued protection? </div><div class="t mce5 xd3 h59 yed9 ff4 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">111 Because everyone is expected to give? </div><div class="t m1d8 xc3 h361 yf77 ffd fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">‚ùë </div><div class="t m855 x16 h59 yce7 ff4 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">To appease one&apos;s conscience? </div><div class="t mf46 x73 h80 y50f ff2 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7 </div><div class="t m1c2 x74 h59 y1010 ff4 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">o </div><div class="t mdd8 xc h59 y100f ff4 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">express love and </div><div class="t m198 x74 h59 ya43 ff4 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ratitude to God? </div><div class="t m34b x74 h80 y1304 ff2 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">r </div><div class="t m1c2 x73 h59 y19c8 ff4 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">o </div><div class="t mdfc x5f h59 y469 ff4 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">hasten the work </div><div class="t m86 x18 h59 y4e3 ff4 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of God in the earth? </div><div class="t mee xc3 ha8 y3a2 ff1 fs25 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">No Other Way </div><div class="t m301 x15 h2d y85e ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;The Lord does not need our </div><div class="t m647 xb4 h2d yef8 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">offerings. We cannot enrich Him by </div><div class="t mdc xb4 h2d y842 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">our gifts. Says the psalmist, &quot;All </div><div class="t md04 xb4 h2d y56e ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">thins come of thee, and of thine </div><div class="t ma08 xb4 h2d y9ad ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">owave we given thee.&quot; </div><div class="t m19b3 xcf h2d y9ad ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Yet God </div><div class="t me9a xb4 h2d y3a8 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">permits us to show our appreciation </div><div class="t m541 xb4 h2d y3db ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of his mercies by self-sactific </div><div class="t m115f xb4 h2d ybd9 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">efforts to extend the same to others. </div><div class="t m646 xb4 h2d y11d0 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">This is the only way in which it is </div><div class="t m1f5 xb4 h2d y40c ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">possible for us to manifest our </div><div class="t m3d9 xb4 h2d y829 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">gratitude and love to God. He </div><div class="t md2a xb4 h2d y52b ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">has provided no other way&quot; </div><div class="t m81a x4 hd1 y801 ff6 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Review and Herald, </div><div class="t m1bb x7e h25 y1206 ff4 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Dec. 6. 1887). </div><div class="t m5a8 x5d h338 y870 ff7 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Express your gratitude this quarter </div><div class="t m1259 x5d h338 y14ee ff7 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">through systematic planned giving. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
